# superficial-duck

## Description
This script performs system checks in windows that could aid in privilege escalation

## Usage
Upload the script to the impacted machine then run it
```
wind0z_Pr1v3sc.bat
```

## Uploading the code via CLI
If you are trying to upload the script via the CLI (evil-winrm) and are having trouble, you can run the command below to upload the data locally
```
[Text.Encoding]::Utf8.GetString([Convert]::FromBase64String('')) | Out-File -FilePath duck.bat

```
